{"tid":1858754,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"美國鑑證科警員證實   Android 手機較 iPhone 更難破解","createTime":"2020-02-03T01:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T11:28:17.000Z","uid":159448,"like":23,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"cb913c4efdd155d9de6ea6b7106920cbdb53fdea","tid":1858754,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T01:48:05.000Z","msg":"智能手機裝著不少個人資料和通訊記錄，當執法機關需要進行調查時，往往都會從疑犯的智能手機入手。近期有不少新聞與 iPhone 被執法機關破解有關，日前有美國負責數碼鑑證的警員就透露，現時的 Android 手機比 iPhone 更難破解。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來自德州 Fort Worth 警區的數碼鑑證探員 Rex Kiser 接受訪問時，表示他們約一年前無法破解 iPhone，但可以破解任何 Android 手機，但現在並非所有 Android 手機都能破解。報導提到執法機構僱用專業的手機破解公司，當中最出名的 Cellebrite 擁有能夠破解包括 iPhone X 在內手機的工具，它能夠抓住 GPS 位置、訊息、通話記錄、聯絡人資訊，甚至 Instagram、Twitter、LinkedIn 等程式的數據，有助進行檢控工作。<br />\n<br />\n報導指 Cellebrite 的工具在對付 Android 手機的加密技術，就未如 iPhone 般成功，例如 Google Pixel 2、Samsung Galaxy S9、華為 P20 Pro 都不對應，無法取得社交媒體、瀏覽或 GPS 資料。雖然 Cellebrite 的工具在 Android 層面比較遜色，但並不代表 Android 無從破解，只是花費的時間和資源較多。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/02/03/android-encryption-forensics/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F02%2F03%2Fandroid-encryption-forensics%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7V1DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=e5755507\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/02/03/android-encryption-forensics/mobile-phone/</a><br />\n<br />\nIfan全面退場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2aaccc141402b259b2a8cb32396f68f648e409","tid":1858754,"uid":343361,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T01:50:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">紅蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"f9419fa69a88e069eaf38df137a328dc01701da7","tid":1858754,"uid":9387,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:02:04.000Z","msg":"我地派個follow開資安嘅vintage都夠吊打呢啲德州警<br />\n騎馬佢就叻"},{"pid":"b51b8f6b4d85c662ce8226fc16a93fb